{
  "stem": "25639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so we would see the people change, or get undressed-- not change, but get undressed-- in front of the gas chamber and crematorium on the beautiful green lawn, as we passed by them to go to work.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We just passed them by, and made a left turn on the other side of the gas chamber and crematorium, and just a few feet, and we were at our work place.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there we sorted-- sorted out the clothes, bundles, and packages that they all-- that we all brought from home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Sometimes this would be an advantage to us, because once in a while we would find food in these packages.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we would supplement our meager diet with these-- with this food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Only then would our calories increase, but we were not permitted to eat any of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so we had to do it very discreetly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But when we found something edible, we found a way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was-- it was an unbelievable place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "People would bring along their best clothes, usually the transports from Hungary, they were the ones that were coming in the next few months.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were-- we were asked to look in the lining of the clothes for hidden jewelry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so we had to feel the shoulder pads, which people wore at that time, and the linings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we very often found diamonds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "People brought along small things, small items that could be easily carried.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they brought-- they probably-- it probably-- they probably were their lifetime savings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is what they were hoping to save their lives with, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] possibly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it all went into a different pile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were these different piles.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
